<!DOCTYPE tmc-service-paragraph SYSTEM "../dtd/paragraph-contents.dtd">
<tmc-service-paragraph><pub id="RM25T0E"><servcat id="_51"><name>Engine / Hybrid System</name><section id="_029760"><name>1VD-FTV ENGINE CONTROL</name><ttl id="_0282525"><name>ECD SYSTEM(w/ DPF)</name><para id="RM100000000YXY8" category="C"><dtccode>P245C</dtccode><dtcname>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Cooler Bypass Control Circuit Low</dtcname><dtccode>P245D</dtccode><dtcname>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Cooler Bypass Control Circuit High</dtcname><subpara id="RM100000000YXY8_01" category="03"><name>DESCRIPTION</name><content5><ptxt>The vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) is controlled by the ECM, and the opening and closing of the EGR cooler bypass valve is performed according to the vacuum applied by the vacuum pump.</ptxt><table type="dtc-explan-table" pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="6"><colspec colname="1" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="2" colwidth="1.13in"/><colspec colname="3" colwidth="1.91in"/><colspec colname="4" colwidth="1.91in"/><colspec colname="5" colwidth="0.71in"/><colspec colname="6" colwidth="0.71in"/><thead><row><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Detection Item</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>MIL</ptxt></entry><entry align="center" valign="middle"><ptxt>Memory</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P245C</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Cooler Bypass Control Circuit Low</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>Open or short in the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) for 3 seconds (1 trip detection logic).</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Open or short in vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) circuit</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve)</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="mil"><ptxt>Comes on</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="memory"><ptxt>DTC stored</ptxt></data-name></entry></row><row><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-code"><ptxt>P245D</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="detect-item"><ptxt>Exhaust Gas Recirculation Cooler Bypass Control Circuit High</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="dtc-detect-cond"><ptxt>Open or short in the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) for 3 seconds (1 trip detection logic).</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="trouble-area"><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Open or short in vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) circuit</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>Vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve)</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>ECM</ptxt></item></list1></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="mil"><ptxt>Comes on</ptxt></data-name></entry><entry align="left" valign="middle"><data-name name="memory"><ptxt>DTC stored</ptxt></data-name></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YXY8_06" category="03"><name>CONFIRMATION DRIVING PATTERN</name><content5><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="2.12in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="4.96in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>DTC Detection Drive Pattern</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P245C</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" morerows="1"><ptxt>Ignition switch ON for 3 seconds or more</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>P245D</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YXY8_02" category="03"><name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name><content5><figure type="1" translate="E"><graphic graphicname="A394574E02" width="7.168479331in" height="3.812598425in"/></figure></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YXY8_03" category="10"><name>CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT</name><content5><atten3><list1 type="unordered"><item><ptxt>Inspect the fuses of circuits related to this system before performing the following inspection procedure.</ptxt></item><item><ptxt>After replacing the ECM, the new ECM needs registration (Click here <mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000Z1DB"/></mlink>) and initialization (Click here <mlink><xref label="Seep00002" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000000YXU9"/></mlink>).</ptxt></item></list1></atten3><atten4><ptxt>Read freeze frame data using the GTS. Freeze frame data records the engine condition when malfunctions are detected. When troubleshooting, freeze frame data can help determine if the vehicle was moving or stationary, if the engine was warmed up or not, and other data from the time the malfunction occurred.</ptxt></atten4></content5></subpara><subpara id="RM100000000YXY8_05" category="01"><name>PROCEDURE</name><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0001" cellposition="1-1"><testtitle>INSPECT VACUUM SWITCHING VALVE ASSEMBLY (FOR EGR BYPASS VALVE)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Inspect the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve).</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="002" href="RM100000001080O"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="1-1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-1" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0006"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="1-4"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-4" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0008"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0006" cellposition="2-1"><testtitle>CHECK VACUUM SWITCHING VALVE ASSEMBLY (FOR EGR BYPASS VALVE) (POWER SOURCE CIRCUIT)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR bypass valve) connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Measure the voltage according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt><spec type="voltage"><title>Standard Voltage</title><table><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.38in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.37in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Switch Condition</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C111-1 - Body ground</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Ignition switch ON</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>11 to 14 V</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec><figure type="1" translate="C"><graphic graphicname="A348992C09" width="3.434793307in" height="3.434793307in"/><callout><table pgwide="0" type="caption-table"><tgroup cols="2"><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="0.69in"/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.75in"/><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>*a</ptxt></entry><entry><ptxt>Front view of wire harness connector</ptxt><ptxt>(to Vacuum Switching Valve Assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve))</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></callout></figure></test1><test1><ptxt>Reconnect the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR bypass valve) connector.</ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="2-1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-1" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0011"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="2-3"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-3" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0002"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0011" cellposition="3-1"><testtitle>CHECK HARNESS AND CONNECTOR (VACUUM SWITCHING VALVE (FOR EGR BYPASS VALVE) - ECM)</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR bypass valve) connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Disconnect the ECM connector.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Measure the resistance according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt><spec type="resistance"><title>Standard Resistance</title><table pgwide="1"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="3.54in"/><colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.77in"/><colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.77in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Condition</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C111-2 (ECBV) - C39-43 (ECBV)</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Below 1 Ω</ptxt></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>C111-2 (ECBV) or C39-43 (ECBV) - Body ground and other terminals</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Always</ptxt></entry><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>10 kΩ or higher</ptxt></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>OK</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="2"><ptxt>NG</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-1"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-1" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0005"/></result><result label="2" cellposition="3-2"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="4-2" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0002"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 5</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0005" cellposition="4-1"><testtitle>REPLACE ECM</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Replace the ECM.</ptxt><ptxt>Click here<mlink><xref label="Seep00001" term-id-from="001" term-id-to="003" href="RM100000000FJHY"/><xref term-id-from="003" href="RM1000000013IGX"/></mlink></ptxt></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="4-1"><action actiontype="jump" cellposition="5-1" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0003"><actiontitle>GO TO STEP 6</actiontitle></action></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0002" cellposition="3-3"><testtitle>REPAIR OR REPLACE HARNESS OR CONNECTOR</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Repair or replace the harness or connector.</ptxt><atten4><ptxt>If the voltage at the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) connector is not 11 to 14 V, repair or replace the harness and connector between the vacuum switching valve assembly (for EGR Bypass Valve) and instrument panel junction block.</ptxt></atten4></test1><spec type="other"><title>Result</title><table><tgroup cols="1"><colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/><thead><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><ptxt>Proceed to</ptxt></entry></row></thead><tbody><row><entry valign="middle" align="center"><judge-value label="1"><ptxt>NEXT</ptxt></judge-value></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></spec></content6><results><result label="1" cellposition="3-3"><action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-3" childid="RM100000000YXY8_05_0003"/></result></results></testgrp><testgrp id="RM100000000YXY8_05_0003" cellposition="4-3"><testtitle>CONFIRM WHETHER MALFUNCTION HAS BEEN SUCCESSFULLY REPAIRED</testtitle><content6><test1><ptxt>Connect the GTS to the DLC3.</ptxt></test1><test1><ptxt>Clear the DTCs.</ptxt><gts-info category="dtc-delete"><title>Powertrain &gt; Engine and ECT &gt; Clear DTCs</title><gts-exec function-id="50002"><gts-ecu ecu-id="234"/></gts-exec><app-communication><app-param name="process-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="edit-mode">1</app-param><app-param name="insert-mode">0</app-param><app-param name="function-tab">0</app-param><app-param name="category-div">1</app-param><app-param name="category-div-name">Powertrain</app-param><app-param name="ecu-id">234</app-param><app-param name="ecu-na